WEBVTT

1
00:01:00.870 --> 00:01:02.330
Now. everyone!

2
00:01:29.770 --> 00:01:32.440
D-Did we win?

3
00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:57.307
These four great warriors aided the
hero and defeated the Demon King!

4
00:01:57.390 --> 00:01:59.307
In recognition of your efforts.

5
00:01:59.390 --> 00:02:02.857
I shall give you. the sages of
Fire. Earth. Water. and Wind.

6
00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:05.940
the titles reserved for
the strongest of mages...

7
00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:08.650
The Four Emperors!

8
00:02:12.270 --> 00:02:13.527
The Four Emperors...

9
00:02:13.610 --> 00:02:20.380
In this world. only those of noble
blood can earn the title "Emperor."

10
00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:25.207
Even if these titles are only
applicable in the world of magic.

11
00:02:25.290 --> 00:02:27.757
they are still being bestowed upon us!

12
00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:30.800
What an incredible reward!

13
00:02:32.220 --> 00:02:33.760
Sage Eftal...

14
00:02:33.970 --> 00:02:34.707
Yes.

15
00:02:34.790 --> 00:02:39.297
In the world of magic. though
you may not be the mightiest.

16
00:02:39.380 --> 00:02:42.477
you still have been given
the title of Emperor.

17
00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:46.270
From now on. you may call yourself
the Lightning Emperor.

18
00:02:47.220 --> 00:02:48.360
Me?

19
00:02:50.250 --> 00:02:52.920
Y-You honor me. sire!

20
00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:58.367
A round of applause for
the new Four Emperors!

21
00:02:58.450 --> 00:03:05.237
Hooray! Hooray for the Four Emperors!
Hooray for the Four Emperors!

22
00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:08.100
After forty years studying magic...

23
00:03:08.570 --> 00:03:14.340
In that moment. my efforts were
recognized in the greatest way possible!

24
00:03:31.210 --> 00:03:32.070
Master Eftal.

25
00:03:32.600 --> 00:03:34.820
breakfast is ready.

26
00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:36.777
Oh...

27
00:03:36.860 --> 00:03:38.330
Good morning. Merlin.

28
00:03:41.110 --> 00:03:43.620
Another good day for training.

29
00:05:21.230 --> 00:05:23.380
Excellent. Keep it up.

30
00:05:28.140 --> 00:05:29.027
Focus!

31
00:05:29.110 --> 00:05:30.517
R-Right!

32
00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.967
If you can't focus. you won't be able to

33
00:05:33.050 --> 00:05:35.410
maintain your magic circle while chanting.

34
00:05:36.970 --> 00:05:38.350
Okay. enough.

35
00:05:39.540 --> 00:05:41.987
Well done. everyone. Keep it up.

36
00:05:42.070 --> 00:05:46.720
- Now. let's try the level
four spells again...

37
00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:46.720
- Master Eftal?

38
00:05:48.280 --> 00:05:51.250
Why don't you get some rest?

39
00:05:57.750 --> 00:06:00.920
Ah. I'm not tired at all.

40
00:06:02.180 --> 00:06:04.930
I see...

41
00:06:17.390 --> 00:06:19.780
A demon mother and her child...

42
00:06:20.750 --> 00:06:23.490
They were caught up in our battle?

43
00:06:28.060 --> 00:06:30.927
You don't remember it. I suspect...

44
00:06:31.010 --> 00:06:34.400
But I killed so many of your clan.

45
00:06:34.830 --> 00:06:38.910
And now you're looking at me
with such worry...

46
00:06:41.040 --> 00:06:44.887
Okay. let's go over our
level four spells again.

47
00:06:44.970 --> 00:06:45.557
Okay.

48
00:06:45.640 --> 00:06:49.120
Master Eftal! Please teach us level six!

49
00:06:50.020 --> 00:06:51.327
Level six?

50
00:06:51.410 --> 00:06:53.667
We just learned level five. though!

51
00:06:53.750 --> 00:06:55.277
As always. Merlin.

52
00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:56.190
you're very spirited.

53
00:06:56.430 --> 00:06:57.667
Of course I am!

54
00:06:57.750 --> 00:07:00.650
I'm the best student of Eftal.
the Lightning Emperor!

55
00:07:04.260 --> 00:07:05.970
The Lightning Emperor...

56
00:07:08.780 --> 00:07:11.410
What's your hurry. Merlin?

57
00:07:12.200 --> 00:07:15.120
Shall we continue practicing
our concentration instead?

58
00:07:15.340 --> 00:07:16.997
The fundamentals are important.

59
00:07:17.080 --> 00:07:18.347
I know!

60
00:07:18.430 --> 00:07:20.830
But I need to hurry...

61
00:07:23.710 --> 00:07:26.470
No. never mind.

62
00:07:43.340 --> 00:07:44.900
I can't be afraid.

63
00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:06.940
A little deeper...

64
00:08:16.010 --> 00:08:18.307
I'll defeat the monster in there

65
00:08:18.390 --> 00:08:21.860
so I can truly call myself the
Lightning Emperor's best student.

66
00:08:22.380 --> 00:08:27.220
Then I can teach everyone so
Master Eftal doesn't have to.

67
00:08:28.310 --> 00:08:32.440
Master Eftal can relax and get some rest.

68
00:08:46.820 --> 00:08:49.550
Level four magic didn't work at all?!

69
00:08:50.560 --> 00:08:52.510
I've got one chance...

70
00:08:54.840 --> 00:08:58.147
Spirits of the wind. dwell in my hands!

71
00:08:58.230 --> 00:08:59.767
Grant me your blessings...

72
00:08:59.850 --> 00:09:01.560
And power.

73
00:09:01.840 --> 00:09:04.687
Gather with the thunder...

74
00:09:04.770 --> 00:09:06.607
And through your pact with me...

75
00:09:06.690 --> 00:09:08.570
Release your light!

76
00:09:09.280 --> 00:09:12.240
Focus! Focus!

77
00:09:13.560 --> 00:09:14.780
Level six!

78
00:09:15.710 --> 00:09:17.120
Thunderbolt!

79
00:09:18.500 --> 00:09:19.330
I did it!

80
00:09:54.670 --> 00:09:56.197
Master Eftal!

81
00:09:56.280 --> 00:10:00.160
I told you to stay away from this forest!

82
00:10:01.710 --> 00:10:03.840
I-I'm sorry!

83
00:10:04.280 --> 00:10:05.540
Sheesh...

84
00:10:06.100 --> 00:10:07.540
Listen. Merlin.

85
00:10:07.980 --> 00:10:11.380
You have the greatest potential
among all my students.

86
00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:13.480
But you're in too much of a hurry.

87
00:10:13.870 --> 00:10:16.517
Power you rush to master
is no power at all.

88
00:10:16.600 --> 00:10:20.100
It'll slip right through your fingers.

89
00:10:21.960 --> 00:10:23.947
I'm in the middle of a lecture.

90
00:10:24.030 --> 00:10:26.730
Don't interrupt me.

91
00:10:26.950 --> 00:10:28.060
Level ten.

92
00:10:29.690 --> 00:10:30.730
Eftal.

93
00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:50.917
Master Eftal was so strong...

94
00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:52.907
That again?

95
00:10:52.990 --> 00:10:57.467
You've done enough study
for today. Go to bed.

96
00:10:57.550 --> 00:10:58.620
Okay!

97
00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:03.460
Master Eftal?!

98
00:11:05.190 --> 00:11:06.900
Damn this sickness...

99
00:11:08.860 --> 00:11:10.270
Master Eftal?

100
00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:12.770
You saw. then?

101
00:11:14.020 --> 00:11:15.550
I noticed before.

102
00:11:17.380 --> 00:11:20.720
That's why I wanted to
learn as fast as I could...

103
00:11:21.400 --> 00:11:24.350
So that's why you've
been working so hard?

104
00:11:25.400 --> 00:11:28.750
Master Eftal. please
take care of yourself.

105
00:11:29.110 --> 00:11:32.237
Get as much rest as you can...

106
00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:35.827
I have little time left.

107
00:11:35.910 --> 00:11:38.680
And no time to rest.

108
00:11:38.900 --> 00:11:39.980
Why?

109
00:11:40.430 --> 00:11:45.480
Why are you still training your
magic even when you're so sick?

110
00:11:47.380 --> 00:11:48.590
Because...

111
00:11:50.100 --> 00:11:55.100
I want to train the talented students
who come after me. like you.

112
00:11:57.830 --> 00:12:01.280
I wanted to be the
strongest in the world.

113
00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:04.860
"Wanted"?

114
00:12:05.210 --> 00:12:06.030
Yes.

115
00:12:06.620 --> 00:12:12.290
Every mage wants to be
the greatest of them all.

116
00:12:12.640 --> 00:12:14.330
I am no exception.

117
00:12:14.870 --> 00:12:15.840
But...

118
00:12:16.250 --> 00:12:22.180
Unfortunately. I'm never
going to achieve that.

119
00:12:22.400 --> 00:12:23.947
What are you saying?

120
00:12:24.030 --> 00:12:26.350
You're incredibly strong!

121
00:12:26.600 --> 00:12:28.977
The Lightning Emperor is
the strongest of them all!

122
00:12:29.060 --> 00:12:35.090
Even today. you did a level
ten spell so... easily...

123
00:12:39.270 --> 00:12:41.870
I know what you're trying to say.

124
00:12:43.790 --> 00:12:47.937
But compared to the younger
ones and their talents...

125
00:12:48.020 --> 00:12:49.100
I...

126
00:12:51.910 --> 00:12:54.210
Even during the battle
against the Demon King.

127
00:12:54.590 --> 00:12:57.860
only I. the oldest. was ever struggling.

128
00:13:09.300 --> 00:13:10.267
Master Eftal!

129
00:13:10.350 --> 00:13:12.780
Big news! Master Eftal!

130
00:13:13.850 --> 00:13:14.857
What is it?

131
00:13:14.940 --> 00:13:18.987
The Flame Emperor has finished
his theory of magical aptitude!

132
00:13:19.070 --> 00:13:19.937
What?

133
00:13:20.020 --> 00:13:21.640
The details are here!

134
00:13:23.520 --> 00:13:28.450
The discovery of one's magical aptitude
has long been thought impossible...

135
00:13:29.370 --> 00:13:30.337
I see!

136
00:13:30.420 --> 00:13:31.670
So that's how it's done?

137
00:13:32.260 --> 00:13:34.910
The Flame Emperor is every
bit the genius I expected.

138
00:13:35.390 --> 00:13:37.517
Master Eftal. what will you do?

139
00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:40.467
It's worth testing. Let's give it a try!

140
00:13:40.550 --> 00:13:41.400
Okay!

141
00:13:43.400 --> 00:13:45.077
There we go.

142
00:13:45.160 --> 00:13:47.427
Let's start with Merlin.

143
00:13:47.510 --> 00:13:48.510
Ow!

144
00:13:51.190 --> 00:13:54.407
You put a single hair from the
test subject in each vial.

145
00:13:54.490 --> 00:13:57.607
immersing it in special magic
water treated for each element:

146
00:13:57.690 --> 00:14:00.240
fire. earth. water. and wind.

147
00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:06.487
The blue and green ones are shining!

148
00:14:06.570 --> 00:14:09.457
What does it mean?

149
00:14:09.540 --> 00:14:13.417
The paper says that the strength of
the light and the depth of the color

150
00:14:13.500 --> 00:14:17.460
indicate a rank between E and S.

151
00:14:17.700 --> 00:14:21.257
Green and blue are glowing
and brightly-colored.

152
00:14:21.340 --> 00:14:25.680
I guess that means you have S
Rank in both Water and Wind.

153
00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:28.967
The other test tubes are red and brown...

154
00:14:29.050 --> 00:14:32.560
So fire is C Rank and
earth is B. is that right?

155
00:14:32.940 --> 00:14:34.907
Yes. so it seems.

156
00:14:34.990 --> 00:14:37.050
I guess that sounds right...

157
00:14:37.940 --> 00:14:39.400
This is amazing.

158
00:14:42.730 --> 00:14:45.827
It doesn't seem to mean much to Merlin.

159
00:14:45.910 --> 00:14:49.120
but I've raised her since
she was a baby. so I know.

160
00:14:49.780 --> 00:14:52.217
Given what I know about
Merlin's magical aptitude.

161
00:14:52.300 --> 00:14:56.000
the results of this magical
aptitude test are 100% accurate.

162
00:14:56.500 --> 00:14:59.057
The current way we learn magic involves

163
00:14:59.140 --> 00:15:04.457
making a student study
basic spells of all types.

164
00:15:04.540 --> 00:15:08.520
and after a certain time. we decide
what we believe their aptitude to be.

165
00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:11.147
But now we'll know the
minute they start school...

166
00:15:11.230 --> 00:15:16.800
No. we'll know what they're best
at the moment they're born!

167
00:15:17.190 --> 00:15:18.750
They can become stronger!

168
00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:22.147
Do me next.

169
00:15:22.230 --> 00:15:24.717
There's no need!

170
00:15:24.800 --> 00:15:27.587
You're one of the Four Emperors!

171
00:15:27.670 --> 00:15:30.840
What. you're not curious. Merlin?

172
00:15:31.370 --> 00:15:33.537
It must be amazing!

173
00:15:33.620 --> 00:15:35.180
I can't wait to see!

174
00:15:35.520 --> 00:15:37.790
To tell the truth. I want to know.

175
00:15:39.550 --> 00:15:42.670
Even if I can't reach the
highest level of magic...

176
00:15:43.340 --> 00:15:46.927
I want to know if I ever
had the talent to do it.

177
00:15:47.010 --> 00:15:48.067
Go ahead.

178
00:15:48.150 --> 00:15:48.930
All right.

179
00:15:51.660 --> 00:15:56.017
I've worked dozens. no. hundreds
of times harder than anyone else!

180
00:15:56.100 --> 00:15:58.060
I'm sure the other Emperors
worked hard too...

181
00:15:58.330 --> 00:16:02.480
But I put in considerably
more effort than they did.

182
00:16:02.750 --> 00:16:03.740
So...

183
00:16:07.900 --> 00:16:09.850
C-Colorless?

184
00:16:11.920 --> 00:16:15.117
Colorless means no aptitude. it says.

185
00:16:15.200 --> 00:16:18.580
But there's no way you
could have zero aptitude!

186
00:16:18.800 --> 00:16:19.657
That's right!

187
00:16:19.740 --> 00:16:20.877
It's impossible!

188
00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:27.427
No aptitude at all means that none
of the spirits will bless you!

189
00:16:27.510 --> 00:16:29.320
B-But why?

190
00:16:29.990 --> 00:16:32.850
I'm the Lightning Emperor!

191
00:16:33.290 --> 00:16:36.357
We may have done it wrong!

192
00:16:36.440 --> 00:16:38.750
Let's try again!

193
00:16:39.440 --> 00:16:41.217
Yes. you're right.

194
00:16:41.300 --> 00:16:42.807
Let's try again.

195
00:16:42.890 --> 00:16:44.880
We must have made a mistake!

196
00:16:47.700 --> 00:16:52.700
But the vials remained colorless
no matter how many times I tried.

197
00:16:54.160 --> 00:16:55.660
Why?

198
00:16:56.510 --> 00:16:57.620
No...

199
00:16:58.030 --> 00:17:02.607
It always took me longer than
the rest to learn magic.

200
00:17:02.690 --> 00:17:08.240
Only my unending effort made
me better than any of them.

201
00:17:08.840 --> 00:17:10.030
I see...

202
00:17:10.550 --> 00:17:12.530
So that's it.

203
00:17:12.900 --> 00:17:15.927
The reason I couldn't beat
the other Emperors...

204
00:17:16.010 --> 00:17:19.850
The reason they continuously
surpassed me...

205
00:17:20.310 --> 00:17:24.200
I had no magical aptitude.

206
00:17:25.070 --> 00:17:26.750
That's the only reason.

207
00:17:27.550 --> 00:17:29.470
It's so simple.

208
00:17:30.830 --> 00:17:32.110
Master Eftal!

209
00:17:34.830 --> 00:17:36.410
Master Eftal...

210
00:17:44.760 --> 00:17:47.567
Master Eftal. I've brought
you some hot water.

211
00:17:47.650 --> 00:17:48.590
Stay out.

212
00:17:54.780 --> 00:17:56.187
I always...

213
00:17:56.270 --> 00:18:00.317
I always thought I could reach the
highest levels of magic someday.

214
00:18:00.400 --> 00:18:05.110
But I couldn't overcome
the wall called "talent."

215
00:18:05.470 --> 00:18:09.620
In that moment. I lost
my wishes and my hope.

216
00:18:10.220 --> 00:18:14.820
No... I had no wishes
or hope from the start!

217
00:18:15.290 --> 00:18:18.987
I'm pathetic... I'm so pathetic!

218
00:18:19.070 --> 00:18:21.657
If only I had more time...

219
00:18:21.740 --> 00:18:26.200
I thought that effort
would get me there...

220
00:18:26.860 --> 00:18:29.630
I'm so frustrated... so frustrated...

221
00:18:30.700 --> 00:18:34.250
So frustrated... so frustrated...

222
00:18:49.710 --> 00:18:52.140
Oh. that's right.

223
00:18:54.240 --> 00:19:00.660
It was over 50 years ago.
I forgot I even had this skill.

224
00:19:00.910 --> 00:19:02.187
This is where we first met.

225
00:19:02.270 --> 00:19:06.120
after I ended my life in a different
world from the last one.

226
00:19:06.630 --> 00:19:09.247
It's been a long time. Eftal.

227
00:19:09.330 --> 00:19:11.047
Your skill. "Indomitable."

228
00:19:11.130 --> 00:19:16.180
gave you the power to work toward
your goal without ever giving up.

229
00:19:16.530 --> 00:19:18.417
So that's it?

230
00:19:18.500 --> 00:19:22.180
That explains why I could never
give up on anything.

231
00:19:22.440 --> 00:19:26.010
Now. it's time for your
second reincarnation.

232
00:19:26.320 --> 00:19:31.060
Again. you may have two
starting bonus skills.

233
00:19:31.420 --> 00:19:34.067
How about "2x Growth"?

234
00:19:34.150 --> 00:19:36.220
No. I'll pass.

235
00:19:38.010 --> 00:19:41.237
I've still got my magical knowledge.

236
00:19:41.320 --> 00:19:45.160
If I have the time to put in effort
and get better. that's enough.

237
00:19:46.490 --> 00:19:48.120
Just what I'd expected to hear.

238
00:19:48.450 --> 00:19:53.257
You rose to the rank of the Four Emperors.
even though you had no aptitude.

239
00:19:53.340 --> 00:19:58.257
That wasn't due to your skill alone.
It was thanks to the strength of your will.

240
00:19:58.340 --> 00:20:01.077
Well. I don't know if I'd go that far.

241
00:20:01.160 --> 00:20:02.517
Very well.

242
00:20:02.600 --> 00:20:05.517
Are you ready. then?

243
00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:08.110
Yes. go ahead.

244
00:20:08.640 --> 00:20:10.780
Have a wonderful journey.

245
00:20:22.500 --> 00:20:26.090
M-My memories are coming
back to me again...

246
00:20:42.070 --> 00:20:44.970
I'm Eftal. the Lightning Emperor!

247
00:20:45.700 --> 00:20:47.337
Eftal!

248
00:20:47.420 --> 00:20:48.327
Good morning!

249
00:20:48.410 --> 00:20:49.297
Did you sleep well?

250
00:20:49.380 --> 00:20:51.890
My beloved Eftal!

251
00:20:50.170 --> 00:20:52.440
Mom! I can't breathe!

252
00:20:52.770 --> 00:20:54.480
Oh. sorry.

253
00:20:56.410 --> 00:20:58.580
Breakfast is ready.

254
00:21:01.540 --> 00:21:05.027
Thanks to the Second Reincarnation
skill that the Goddess gave me.

255
00:21:05.110 --> 00:21:07.580
I'm now on my third life.

256
00:21:08.230 --> 00:21:13.420
Ever since I turned four. memories of
the old Eftal have started to return.

257
00:21:13.950 --> 00:21:16.610
This time. I'm going
to truly master magic.

258
00:21:18.420 --> 00:21:19.797
What is it?

259
00:21:19.880 --> 00:21:22.820
Oh. nothing!

260
00:21:21.860 --> 00:21:23.580
- What I remembered this morning

261
00:21:22.830 --> 00:21:24.620
- Thank you!

262
00:21:23.580 --> 00:21:26.330
- was how to prepare water
for a magical aptitude test.

263
00:21:26.810 --> 00:21:28.740
Okay. time to try it!

264
00:21:36.630 --> 00:21:38.570
I knew to expect it. but...

265
00:21:43.630 --> 00:21:47.340
No color at all. huh?

266
00:21:48.110 --> 00:21:51.437
It's likely I'm going to hit my limits

267
00:21:51.520 --> 00:21:56.750
when I learn level ten spells.
just like last time.

268
00:21:59.040 --> 00:22:00.130
A dragon?!

269
00:22:02.070 --> 00:22:04.117
Its eyes are crimson!

270
00:22:04.200 --> 00:22:06.180
Someone made it mad?

271
00:22:09.800 --> 00:22:12.397
Hey. the dragon's heading for the capital!

272
00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:13.207
This is bad! After it!

273
00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:14.117
Don't let it get away!

274
00:22:14.200 --> 00:22:15.940
The town's in danger!

275
00:22:19.520 --> 00:22:20.657
That's right...

276
00:22:20.740 --> 00:22:22.907
I could have done something at my peak.

277
00:22:22.990 --> 00:22:25.950
But now I'm just four years old.
What can I do?

278
00:22:31.870 --> 00:22:33.347
If I'd known this would happen.

279
00:22:33.430 --> 00:22:36.520
I would've been reborn in a
body that could use magic.

280
00:22:37.070 --> 00:22:38.187
That's right...

281
00:22:38.270 --> 00:22:40.160
That old spell I made.

282
00:22:40.670 --> 00:22:43.157
My own original spell.

283
00:22:43.240 --> 00:22:45.920
Level ten. Eftal.

284
00:23:06.760 --> 00:23:08.940
I-I did it!

285
00:23:10.990 --> 00:23:12.547
The dragon fell to the ground!

286
00:23:12.630 --> 00:23:14.517
Was it struck by lightning?!

287
00:23:14.600 --> 00:23:15.487
This way!

288
00:23:15.570 --> 00:23:16.960
Be careful!

289
00:23:19.180 --> 00:23:20.840
Does this mean...

290
00:23:28.110 --> 00:23:33.087
It looks like I was reborn into
this world able to wield

291
00:23:33.170 --> 00:23:38.190
magical abilities from the peak
of my old life. even at the age of four.
